'''Nebula Manufacturing''' was one of three large and influential companies based on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Nebula Manufacturing was located deep below [[The Works/Legends|The Works]] in [[Grungeon Block]]. The company was one of the largest businesses on Coruscant during the height of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]].

